IRPact_modellierung.distributions

Class COLTDiscreteDistribution

  • java.lang.Object
    • IRPact_modellierung.distributions.Distribution
      • IRPact_modellierung.distributions.UnivariateDistribution
        • IRPact_modellierung.distributions.DiscreteDistribution
          • IRPact_modellierung.distributions.COLTDiscreteDistribution
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    NegativeBinomialDistribution, PoissonDistribution, ZipfianDistribution

    public abstract class COLTDiscreteDistribution
extends DiscreteDistribution
    Abstraction for discrete distributions based on the COLT library. Includes a random engine since all implementations make use of this (since they are based on the COLT library). Should be generalized in further versions.
